.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Food: peas, artichoke, corn, kale, cranberry
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Cigar: peasmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Nationality:british == Food:corn
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Food:artichoke is on the left of Food:kale
5. Food:artichoke == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:bird
7. Food:cranberry == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:peasmaster == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:prince
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Food:peas
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
